VALUES (@p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19);
SELECT [Id]
FROM [Posts]
WHERE @@ROWCOUNT = 1 AND [Id] = scope_identity();"
